50|$|The {{head tube}} {{contains}} the headset, the interface with the fork. The top tube connects the head <b>tube</b> to the <b>seat</b> <b>tube</b> at the top. The top tube may be positioned horizontally (parallel to the ground), {{or it may}} slope downwards towards the <b>seat</b> <b>tube</b> for additional stand-over clearance. The down tube connects the head tube to the bottom bracket shell.|$|R
